---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import mobileShot from "../../../assets/mobile/mobile-1.png";
import desktopShot from "../../../assets/desktop/desktop-1.png";
---

<section id="home" class="v2-hero" aria-labelledby="v2-hero-title">
  <div class="v2-wrap v2-hero__grid">
    <div class="v2-hero__copy">
      <p class="v2-eyebrow">Whole-site redesign</p>
      <h1 id="v2-hero-title" class="v2-hero__title">
        Bring the refined theme over <em>wholesale</em>, then tune the last 20%.
      </h1>
      <p class="v2-hero__lead">
        The V2 direction keeps Astro, adopts the richer art direction you like,
        and rebuilds the site around a homepage that can market Mythic now and
        support a broader official app line later.
      </p>
      <div class="v2-hero__actions">
        <a class="v2-btn v2-btn--primary" href="#app-family">See app-family structure</a>
        <a class="v2-btn v2-btn--ghost" href="#docs-handoff">See docs handoff</a>
      </div>
      <ul class="v2-stat-list" role="list">
        <li><strong>Astro</strong><span>stays</span></li>
        <li><strong>Whole-site</strong><span>redesign scope</span></li>
        <li><strong>Close fidelity</strong><span>to the source theme</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="v2-stage" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="v2-stage__slab"></div>
      <article class="v2-stage__card v2-stage__card--front">
        <span class="v2-stage__label">Flagship now</span>
        <div class="v2-stage__image">
          <Image src={mobileShot} alt="" widths={[320]} sizes="320px" loading="eager" />
        </div>
        <h2>Mythic GME Mobile</h2>
        <p>Fast solo play on the go, kept front-and-center while the site grows into a broader studio surface.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="v2-stage__card v2-stage__card--back">
        <span class="v2-stage__label">Portfolio later</span>
        <div class="v2-stage__image v2-stage__image--wide">
          <Image src={desktopShot} alt="" widths={[480]} sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 480px" loading="eager" />
        </div>
        <h2>Mythic GME Digital and beyond</h2>
        <p>The new homepage structure, cards, and app rails are being planned for a broader official line.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
